OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fchilly evening to come. However,
OL,7,Fovernight cloud will thicken from the
OL,8,Fwest during the second half of the
OL,9,Fnight with some patchy rain and
OL,10,Fdrizzle developing during the early
OL,11,Fhours, this mostly over the hills.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA dull and damp start to the
OL,14,Fday. However, it should become drier
OL,15,Fand brighter through the morning with
OL,16,Fa few sunny spells developing for the
OL,17,Fafternoon. Feeling warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
